{"tid":1230943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日香港人好團結","createTime":"2019-06-16T10:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T16:14:26.000Z","uid":102267,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6ce8d32a625305b458f2654d6dee6b884fd3cd","tid":1230943,"uid":102267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"希望琴晚個位巴打見到"},{"pid":"3a62bf94e2862180c474bffd7cc1d7ff5c38a027","tid":1230943,"uid":223353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"今日真係好感動，每次有人唔舒服都自動波幫手搵救護，互相合作讓開條路。口號雖多，但學生無暴動好清晰表達。<br />\n<br />\n香港人仍然好多唔係冷感。我睇到香港𥌓光。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6QHV7n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh6QHV7n.png&h=c055187f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd133b77f2178050b7c96c5da67032f32b54de57","tid":1230943,"uid":102267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"行到太古見到鄺仔，佢真係好努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cc788c7e62b3e43881e53805a7e18f8f8258bf","tid":1230943,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:26:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n繼續做野 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=fe7dea0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0bfccb7c8bcdea7a065d14721142af4f224afb26","tid":1230943,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a7733002f5588a5fc4a1d470bd5829a76359f727","tid":1230943,"uid":102267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"TVB 新聞 是是但但"},{"pid":"c54b403d638c82b1e012555b7c72856da08e5c26","tid":1230943,"uid":183674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"今晚我地都喺梁凌傑"}]}